a mini backpack and matching lunch box; Both bags feature cute Hello Kitty graphics</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">STURDY ZIP CLOSURE - Lunch bag and backpack both come with a top carry handle and features a sturdy zip closures to keep lunches warm or cool and accessories organized when not in use</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ONE SIZE FITS MOST - Lunch box measures 9” x 3” x 8” and the mini backpack measures 11” tall, the perfect size for bringing to school, play dates or while traveling; Small size is great for little hands</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SAFE FOR KIDS - Made of high-quality, durable material that is safe for children ages 3 and up; Spot clean and let air dry as needed</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS - Officially licensed Sanrio (Hello Kitty); Dimensions: 9” x 8” x 3” (lunch bag), 11” tall (backpack); Zip closure: yes; Spot clean as needed; Carry handle type: top</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>Hello Kitty 2pc Mini Backpack and Lunch Box Set School Bags for Girls 3 and Up</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">39.99</span></h2>\n                <p>Get ready to bring some Hello Kitty magic to every school day with this officially licensed Sanrio 2pc Hello Kitty School Set! Packed with fun, style, and practicality, this adorable set includes a matching mini backpack and lunch bag, both featuring the super-cute, iconic Hello Kitty design that every fan will love!</p><p><br></p><p>The mini backpack is just the right size for little hands, measuring 11” tall - perfect for carrying school supplies, toys, or accessories. The matching lunch bag (9” x 3” x 8”) keeps snacks fresh and fun, while its sturdy zip closure ensures everything stays secure and organized.</p><p>Both the backpack and lunch bag come with durable, easy-to-use zip closures. Keep lunches warm or cool and store school essentials in the backpack. Whether heading to class, a picnic, or a family trip, these bags make it easy to stay organized and stylish. Plus, the top carry handles make them easy to grab and go - no more struggling with bulky bags!</p><p>The lunch bag and mini backpack are both the perfect size for children ages 3 and up. Lightweight, functional, and packed with charm, it’s the ultimate combo for school or travel.</p><p>Made from high-quality materials, this set is not only safe for kids, but also built to last through all the adventures of the school year. When it’s time to clean, simply spot clean and air dry - it’s that easy!</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n     